::Epyon::

He came to Iron Raptors side. She wouldn't know him but she seemed to be
the commander, so he would guard her.

::Hot Rod::

He kept going for Prime. He opened a commlink, to IR.
"Iron Raptor, this is Hot Rod. I have a chance to stop Dark Prime. Maybe
turn him back to good. I'd like to have Angel Prime with me, for the
Matrix. Do I have permission to continue with this mission or not?"
